MT in ToV or other high end areas and you won't live long enough to hit evade! Though don't worry, this weapon even if a Rogue has will be quickly replaced once you get a Primal Spear / Lightning Claw Combo or the Dagger off of Vulak. Remember this is a team game, you want the warrior to hold agro, and we as warriors want you to do the most damage that you can, as defensive only lasts 2 minutes and its up to you to really rack up the damage. A rogue demanding this weapon is as silly as a monk demanding a SoD! Trust me, there are a TON of better items out there for your class. Most of the high end raid you will see involves only the MT, 2-4th MT using Proc'ing weapons, the rest of the melee will be using non-procing weapons or primal as their only proc'r, it's that important for the MT to hold agro.<br><br><br>Anyways, not flaming any class, just giving you the perspective of high end guild on the way WE handle the item and how well it performs.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>The funeral rite is never Macabre.&nbsp;&nbsp;Death is only the beginning.  Love never dies.</td></tr>
